title: 120 - Big Mitt Episode
description: On today's show, the guys give Mitt some time to catch everybody up with what is going on his life, as we have several Mitt centric questions being asked by the listeners. The guys also go through a loaded Pod FOD that covers a variety of subjects and topics and end the episode with a special Super Bowl edition of Maraldo's Madlibs. Don't forget to send your questions and submissions to the Pod FOD into @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. We appreciate the hell out of all of you for listening, enjoy Super Bowl Sunday, we'll see you Monday.
